---
import Section from '../common/Section.astro';
---

<Section id="about">
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center">
    <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-6 animate-on-scroll">About Me</h2>

    <div class="space-y-4 text-lg leading-relaxed animate-on-scroll animation-delay-100">
      <p>
        I'm a highly accomplished Senior Software Engineer with expertise in architecting and
        developing scalable, cloud-native applications. I specialize in full-stack development,
        microservices architecture, and event-driven systems that handle high-throughput operations.
      </p>

      <p>
        Throughout my career, I've led the development of complex distributed systems, including
        platforms processing over 5,000 events per second. My experience spans across various
        industries - from fintech and e-commerce to media and industrial platforms.
      </p>

      <p>
        I'm passionate about Domain-Driven Design, API-first architectures, and leveraging cloud
        technologies (AWS, Azure) to build robust, maintainable solutions. I thrive in remote
        environments, collaborating with cross-functional teams across multiple time zones.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-12 grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-8 animate-on-scroll animation-delay-200">
      <div class="text-center">
        <div class="text-3xl font-bold gradient-text">9+</div>
        <div class="text-sm text-secondary mt-1">Years Experience</div>
      </div>
      <div class="text-center">
        <div class="text-3xl font-bold gradient-text">5000+</div>
        <div class="text-sm text-secondary mt-1">Events/Second</div>
      </div>
      <div class="text-center">
        <div class="text-3xl font-bold gradient-text">20+</div>
        <div class="text-sm text-secondary mt-1">Microservices</div>
      </div>
      <div class="text-center">
        <div class="text-3xl font-bold gradient-text">25+</div>
        <div class="text-sm text-secondary mt-1">Technologies</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Section>
